These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
There 2 different types of food: cucumber, lime
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, russian
City: edinburgh, prague
House: wooden, palace
1. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the palace house##1
3. the indonesian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Food       | lime       | cucumber |
| Nationality         | russian | indonesian  |
| City       | prague    | edinburgh    |
| House   | palace       | wooden      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: taxi, train
2 different pets are kept: bird, turtle
House: colonial, cape-cod
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, bongani
1. the colonial house is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
3. the colonial house is on the right of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Transport      | train     | taxi |
| Pet           | bird | turtle      |
| House   | cape-cod  | colonial      |
| Cigar         | tiparillo | bongani     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, satire
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, tulip
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, filmmaking
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, february
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Movie-Genre      | disaster | satire  |
| Flower          | zinnia    | tulip   |
| Hobby   | filmmaking  | magic-tricks   |
| Birthday     | february     | may |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
2 different games are played: poker, bridge
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, fonseca
House: art-deco, tower
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
2. the art-deco house is on the right of the person playing poker##1
3. the person playing bridge is the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Game      | poker       | bridge |
| Cigar          | fonseca         | tiparillo    |
| House           | tower | art-deco    |
| Sport   | basketball           | ice-hockey   |

