The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, superhero
City: liverpool, marseilles
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the italian##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | american         | italian    |
| Movie-Genre       | superhero     | sports  |
| City      | liverpool | marseilles     |
| Sport        | ice-hockey     | golf |

