.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-10::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, june
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, jet-ski
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, havana
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, biathlon
1. the havana-smoker is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Birthday          | december | june |
| Transport   | skateboard     | jet-ski      |
| Cigar   | bolivar | havana    |
| Sport           | ice-hockey    | biathlon    |

