1. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
2. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the thai##1
3. the havana-smoker is the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| City           | colone | miami     |
| Food   | cucumber          | radish |
| Cigar           | havana          | chaman    |
| Nationality     | thai            | argentine       |

 